# Question Answering with Research Paper Lookup
This repository implements a thoughtful research assistant that can be used to answer research questions. The assistant will look up relevant papers on arxiv and answer the question with information contained in the papers. The assistant will break down complex questions into sub-questions and answer them one by one.

Made with ❤️ by AIQL

# Usage
Main usage:
```
cd src
python agent_pdf_tool_test.py "What is Batch Normalization?" --dig-deep --doc-store ../docs.pkl
```

